snippet.title: Digimon All-Star Rumble - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
It's time to Digivolve again! Bandai Namco Games is proud to announce Digimon All-Star Rumble for the Xbox 360 and PS3 coming 11.11.14!

Learn more about Digimon All-Star Rumble: http://bit.ly/1nWwpFH and stay tuned for more information!

Follow Bandai Namco Games:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BandaiNamcoUS
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BandaiNamcoUS/
